name: Talon-Tastic Takeout: Osprey Scores the Sashimi
overview:
Osprey in Baja California Sur, Mexico showcase their parenting skills.

The feeding of osprey chicks by their parents is an essential aspect of their altricial development. This process involves the adult ospreys providing a fish-based diet, crucial for the rapid growth and neurological development of their offspring. The nutritional content and abundance of specific fish species directly influence the health, survival rates, and fledging time of osprey chicks.

Filmed in 5K 360.

Filmed in collaboration with Nakawe Project, a conservation non-profit in Baja California focused on the preservation of vital ecosystems and species.

https://nakaweproject.org/
